data.metadata: {"description":"Val_ is an OG Abstract; he was present during the Abstract testnet. He and the team behind Ozy were the first to launch a collection on the Abstract Testnet.\n\nHe is very active within the ecosystem, using almost all of the apps offered today on Abstract and supporting them on X. He is an honest person who is not afraid to support what he loves."}

translation.translatedDescription:
Val_ is an OG Abstract; he was present during the Abstract testnet. He and the team behind Ozy were the first to launch a collection on the Abstract Testnet.

He is very active within the ecosystem, using almost all of the apps offered today on Abstract and supporting them on X. He is an honest person who is not afraid to support what he loves.

data.metadata: {"description":"He is an active member of the Smol Talk community; I often see him stepping in to provide alphas during Spaces. It's always interesting to read his comments.\n\nHe is an active gigachad within the Abstract community, always there to help others, a true GIGACHAD."}

translation.translatedDescription:
He is an active member of the Smol Talk community; I often see him stepping in to provide alphas during Spaces. It's always interesting to read his comments.

He is an active gigachad within the Abstract community, always there to help others, a true GIGACHAD.

He is truly dedicated to Abstract. He's a member of the Abstract community who is really hungry, he's constantly digging on the chain looking for opportunities, and they spread the good word everywhere he can.

He's really a member of the community that every community would love to have.

His devotion has been rewarded, knowing that today he is a Gigachad, and in my opinion, it is well deserved.

He introduced me to the Oekaki ecosystem, and I can't thank him enough for that.

Being a big fan of Japanese culture, I really fell in love with the latest collection they're releasing.

Apart from that, PandyBear is a very active person on the Abstract discord, committed to making the community a better place, and not afraid to say things frankly, which is exactly what I like about him. He's not afraid of hurting people's feelings, he says what he thinks.

data.metadata: {"description":"Envok knows what he's talking about, and I've often seen him discuss highly technical topics on our ecosystem for hours on end, without faltering and bringing real value to his arguments. He's a real OG of web3."}

translation.translatedDescription: Envok knows what he's talking about, and I've often seen him discuss highly technical topics on our ecosystem for hours on end, without faltering and bringing real value to his arguments. He's a real OG of web3.

data.metadata: {"description":"L0K0 is a real OG on Abstract, he launched the first NFT collection on Abstract, during the Testnet, the collection was innovative with a new IP, is also difficult to deploy especially when you are the first to launch.\nHumanly he is a serious and professional person."}

translation.translatedDescription: L0K0 is a real OG on Abstract. He launched the first NFT collection on Abstract during the Testnet. The collection was innovative with a new IP and was also difficult to deploy, especially when you are the first to launch. Humanly, he is a serious and professional person.

data.metadata: {"description":"Il est clip plus vite que son ombre, Il est reconnu pour son talent à saisir les moments les plus importants d'un stream  et à les proposer ensuite au format clip. Il est très impliqué dans la vie de communauté sur Abstract."}

He has an undeniable talent for this activity, but he should not be reduced solely to this activity. He is very involved in community life on Abstract.

data.metadata: {"description":"Quel homme, il était Gigachad, il a perdu le rôle car il a été inactif durant une période, c'est pas pour autant qu'il a abandonné, il a mis les bouchées doubles et récupérer son rôle Gigachad. data.metadata: {"description":"J'ai rencontré Sillybilly la première fois lorsque il a prit contact avec moi via X pour me féliciter du travail que j'ai realisé sur Abstract, il était admiratif de mon travail et j'étais vraiment agréablement surpris de ce retour positif. \n\nPeu de temps après, après un travail acharné il a fini par être rank up Gigachad, c'était amplement merité car Sillybilly est un vrai acharné, c'est un membre de la communauté Abstract qui a vraiment investis de son temps et de sa personne pour rendre la communauté meilleure."}

{"description":"MIC is a rare example of someone who pushes culture forward while getting the day-to-day done. Always on the ground, he leads substantive discussions, explains complex topics clearly, and carefully onboards people from web2 to the chain. His superpower is connecting communities and people: he initiates collaborations, keeps projects updated, helps with launches, and never loses focus on quality. He’s always kind and responsive, yet disciplined and reliable—if he takes it on, he delivers and owns responsibility. I’d especially highlight his contribution to the local Vietnamese community: consistent presence, trust, and growing engagement. If you need a CM/ambassador who brings real value, boosts visibility, and builds a healthy culture, MIC is exactly that."}

data.metadata:
{"description":"J’ai découvert PAVIL grâce à son art, et ce fut une véritable révélation.
Son talent est incroyable : les fresques qu’il réalise sont d’une richesse et d’une précision qui laissent sans voix. Chaque détail raconte une histoire, chaque couleur est choisie avec soin, et l’ensemble dégage une émotion rare.

Mais ce qui rend PAVIL encore plus admirable, c’est sa personnalité. Au-delà de son immense talent, c’est quelqu’un de chaleureux, humble et bienveillant, toujours prêt à partager sa passion et à encourager les autres. Travailler ou échanger avec lui est un vrai plaisir.

Découvrir son travail, c’est bien plus qu’admirer de l’art : c’est ressentir la passion et l’énergie qu’il met dans chacune de ses créations."}

translation.translatedDescription:
I discovered PAVIL through his art, and it was a true revelation.
His talent is incredible: the frescoes he creates are of a richness and precision that leave you speechless. Each detail tells a story, each color is chosen with care, and the whole exudes a rare emotion.

But what makes PAVIL even more admirable is his personality. Beyond his immense talent, he is someone warm, humble, and kind, always ready to share his passion and encourage others. Working or interacting with him is a real pleasure.

Discovering his work is much more than admiring art: it is feeling the passion and energy he puts into each of his creations.

{"description":"Marianne is an incredible giga.
You can tell she was born for the Web3 world — she moves through it like a fish in water.
She radiates an amazing aura and influence on Abstract, and is highly respected by many actors in the ecosystem.

Her strength? Humility and approachability.
What I especially appreciate about her is that she doesn’t try to influence others just to grow her own bags. She’s here to share her passion: the projects she loves, the ones she wants to support, or those she actively participates in.

I admire the kindness and authenticity she brings to everything she does."}

translation.translatedDescription:
Marianne is an incredible giga. You can tell she was born for the Web3 world — she moves through it like a fish in water. She radiates an amazing aura and influence on Abstract, and is highly respected by many actors in the ecosystem.

Her strength? Humility and approachability. What I especially appreciate about her is that she doesn’t try to influence others just to grow her own bags. She’s here to share her passion: the projects she loves, the ones she wants to support, or those she actively participates in.

I admire the kindness and authenticity she brings to everything she does.

data.metadata: {"description":"I have been following Skarly since 2024 and joined OCH as one of the earliest participants, and during this time I have seen him methodically turn an idea into a product while keeping a high standard. He is a rare kind of builder who does the work himself, engages with the community, explains decisions clearly, and iterates quickly. Most importantly he does everything with heart, and you can feel it in the details of the game design and onchain logic. OCH feels cohesive and genuinely excellent, a product you want to return to, which is why it keeps gaining more fans. I like everything Skarly is doing and I am confident he will continue to raise the bar for onchain gaming."}

translation.translatedDescription: I have been following Skarly since 2024 and joined OCH as one of the earliest participants, and during this time I have seen him methodically turn an idea into a product while keeping a high standard. He is a rare kind of builder who does the work himself, engages with the community, explains decisions clearly, and iterates quickly. Most importantly he does everything with heart, and you can feel it in the details of the game design and onchain logic. OCH feels cohesive and genuinely excellent, a product you want to return to, which is why it keeps gaining more fans. I like everything Skarly is doing and I am confident he will continue to raise the bar for onchain gaming.
